data.description: Perfect For Move-Up & Relocation Buyers! 11353 SW Meadowlark Ln in Beaverton Is Located At The Top Of Murrayhill On a 1/2 Acre Private Lot! Updated To Perfection With Casual Elegance + Big Backyard Alongside Greenspace. Stunning Gourmet Kitchen w/ Solid Wood Cabinets Features An Enormous Island As An Ideal Gathering Spot. Open Layout Is Highlighted By Wide Plank Wood Floors, Crisp White Woodwork & Designer Lighting. Fall In Love w/ Gorgeous French Doors Off Dining Room To Extend Entertaining Space Outdoors. Sun-Filled Family Room Opens To An Oversized Deck w/ Gazebo. Grand Primary Suite Is Accented By High Ceilings & Spacious Bathroom. Plenty Of Flex Space w/ Main Floor Office & Bonus Rm/4th Bedrm w/ Skylight & Closet. Extra Large 2-Car Garage Has 6 ft of Extra Space For Workbench, Gym, Storage. Truly a Special Home In Beaverton's Best Neighborhood. The Murrayhill Lifestyle Offers Parks, Trails, Schools, Restaurants & Shops All Within Blocks!
